original_title: Iggy and The Stooges: Live in Sydney
overview: Iggy and the Stooges, live at The Hordern Pavilion in Sydney on April 2, 2013. It was an old-school punk party complete with stage invasions, crazy crowdsurfing and an arsenal of punk anthems – it’s Iggy and The Stooges‘ scorching Sydney show!
title: Iggy and The Stooges: Live in Sydney
